" stop stretching pinkie
im <silent> <M-i> _
im <silent> <M-r> -

" same but with Cmd on Mac
im <silent> <D-i> _
im <silent> <D-r> -

" hashrocket (e.g. ruby, ecmascript)
im <C-h> <Space>=><Space>

" arrow (e.g. elm, haskell)
im <C-g> <Space>-><Space>

" go to last edit location with ,.
nn ,. '.

" jump to line and column by typing '<mark_char>
nn ' `
nn ` '

nn <silent> // :nohlsearch<CR>
